{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father got a shave there at the barber shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a sausage factory, which had a little store open.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were selling sausage by the yard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a big basket and Polish kielbasa sausage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a guy who was selling it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we bought, I don't know, a yard or two yards of the sausage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we bought some bread because we had been hungry terribly-- in a bakery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a whole loaf of bread, and we had some sausage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went back to the railroad stations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It turned out there was no train going to that place where I-- where the farm was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we hopped on the next train which came by, which was a freight train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And really, instead of getting closer to my mother, we were getting farther away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then, we came to a station where there was again a railroad junction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a train going in that direction where mother was supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This time it was nice passenger cars, so comfortable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was one guy who was running-- we watched.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were moving and standing, moving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every time, a plane was showing up-- a German plane was doing this strange stop, then everybody hopped out into the ditches.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a guy there with a-- some medal on his civilian suit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said, I had to be two hours ago, with the general staff in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he never got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, we stopped in one city for about two days, probably, day and a half.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
